  "text": "Sensor fusion can be used to create virtual or 'soft sensors'. Soft sensors or virtual sensors can be used to boost process understanding achievable from available hardware. For one reason or another, the sensors used in a process control approach have limitations such as poor accuracy, poor field of measurement, or perhaps the parameter we want to measure cannot be measured due to limited budget, extreme process conditions or nonexistence of sensor technology [CITATION_1] .",
